text: Lucia Focque (born 30 March 1964) is a Belgian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belgium Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Willebroek
